Package net.sourceforge.metware.binche.graph

Interface Summary
ChEBIGraphPruner Interface that defines the facade of algorithms that process the ChebiGraph to prune it.
PrunningStrategy Defines the main behaviour of a prunning strategy, which is a set of pruners applied in a particular manner.
 

Class Summary
Abstract3PhasePruningStrategy Abstract class which holds most of the relevant control flow for pruning strategies of 3 phases (pre-loop, loop, and final phases).
AllHighPValuePruner This pruner inspects all nodes and removes those with p-value above the set threshold.
ChebiEdge Edge of the ChebiGraph, which is used to store the result of the enrichment analysis in a graph based structure.
ChebiGraph Class providing access to a directed graph plus visualisation functionality required to write and display the graph.
ChebiVertex Vertex of the ChebiGraph, which is used to store the result of the enrichment analysis in a graph based structure.
ColorGradient Utility class to return a shade of red based on the linear function calculated from the input values.
EmptyPruningStrategy Container for pruning strategy with no prunning.
FragmentEnrichPruningStrategy Pruning strategy (a set of pruning objects set as either pre loop, loop and final) designed for the weighted enrichment analysis of fragments.
HighPValueBranchPruner This pruner looks for branches of the ontology in the enrichment analysis result graph which have only high p-values, and gets rid of them.
LinearBranchCollapserPruner This pruner searches for linear branches in the graph (that is, no vertex protrude from a linear path), to collapse them into an initial and final node.
MoleculeLeavesPruner This prunner inspects the graph, descending to the leaves and removing any leave that it is a defined molecule, and not a class but a defined molecule.
PlainEnrichPruningStrategy Pruning strategy (a set of pruning objects set as either pre loop, loop and final) designed for the plain enrichment analysis.
PngWriter Writes the ChEBI enrichment analysis graph, through an image server, as a png file.
RootChildrenPruner This pruner aims to delete the roots (the more general entities in the ontology) and its children up to a defined level.
SpanningForest<ChebiVertex,ChebiEdge> For the input Graph, creates a MinimumSpanningTree using a variation of Prim's algorithm.
SpanningTree<ChebiVertex,ChebiEdge>  
SvgWriter Class to write out JUNG graphs to SVG.
WeightedEnrichPruningStrategy Prunning strategy devised for the weighted enrichment analysis.
ZeroDegreeVertexPruner This pruner removes vertices that have zero degree (considering incoming and outgoing edges).
